description: Julia's Sweets Truck is the expansion of a successful bakery in Tennessee. The bakery reputation has lived on through all its delicious sweet pastries and taking on any task of creating out-of-this-world custom cake decorations. As a mobile bakery they are capable of bringing you the same satisfaction in a large cupcake selection and other sweet pastries. Adding sweet smiles with every bite!
name: Julia's Sweets Truck
